To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private InvertedHammer _invertedhammer;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_invertedhammer = InvertedHammer(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_invertedhammer.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "invertedhammer", _invertedhammer.Current.Value);
}
